<script>
let running = false;
let interval = null;
let stages = [];
let stageIndex = 0;
let timeLeft = 0;
let audioCtx = null;

const timeEl = document.getElementById("time");
const stateEl = document.getElementById("state");
const startBtn = document.getElementById("start");

function beep(freq = 800) {
  if (document.getElementById("mute").checked) return;
  if (!audioCtx) audioCtx = new (window.AudioContext || window.webkitAudioContext)();
  const osc = audioCtx.createOscillator();
  const gain = audioCtx.createGain();
  osc.frequency.value = freq;
  gain.gain.value = 0.15;
  osc.connect(gain);
  gain.connect(audioCtx.destination);
  osc.start();
  osc.stop(audioCtx.currentTime + 0.15);
}

function startTimer() {
  stages = [
    { name: "SETUP", time: +pre.value, beep: 700 },
    { name: "HOT", time: +heat.value, beep: 1100 },
    { name: "COOLING", time: +cool.value, beep: 600 },
    { name: "READY", time: 0, beep: 1400 }
  ];

  stageIndex = 0;
  timeLeft = stages[0].time;
  stateEl.textContent = stages[0].name;
  timeEl.textContent = timeLeft;

  interval = setInterval(tick, 1000);
}

function tick() {
  if (!running) return;

  timeLeft--;
  timeEl.textContent = timeLeft;

  if (timeLeft <= 0) {
    beep(stages[stageIndex].beep);
    stageIndex++;

    if (stageIndex >= stages.length) {
      stopTimer(true);
      return;
    }

    stateEl.textContent = stages[stageIndex].name;
    timeLeft = stages[stageIndex].time;
    timeEl.textContent = timeLeft;
  }
}

function stopTimer(finished = false) {
  clearInterval(interval);
  running = false;
  startBtn.textContent = "START";

  if (finished) {
    stateEl.textContent = "READY";
    timeEl.textContent = "";
  } else {
    stateEl.textContent = "STOPPED";
    timeEl.textContent = "0";
  }
}

startBtn.onclick = () => {
  if (running) {
    stopTimer(false);
    return;
  }

  // Required user interaction for audio in Chromium
  if (!audioCtx) audioCtx = new (window.AudioContext || window.webkitAudioContext)();

  running = true;
  startBtn.textContent = "STOP";
  startTimer();
};
